# 4. Fetch Stories UX Improvement

Currently only one Fetch Stories button exists.

This creates confusion because users sometimes want fresh data while other times they simply want to reuse already generated reports.

Introduce two clearly distinguishable options.

---

## Soft Fetch

Purpose:

Load Stories already available in the local database.

Do NOT call iTrack.

Use cached/generated data.

---

## Force Fetch

Purpose:

Ignore cached data.

Call iTrack again.

Refresh stories from source.

Persist newly retrieved data.

---

## Components

Apply the same concept.

Soft Fetch

↓

Load existing Components from DB.

Force Fetch

↓

Call GitHub.

Reload components.

Update DB.

---

